name: tenebris cor traiecit
description:
When I layed my head on her chest
I heard the most beatiful
And Strong song I ever heard
The most quiet place in the hole world
Make me peaceful
Make wanna live an entire life
I don't wanna go anywhere else
There is the place where I wanna spend the rest of my life.

On her heart beats, I hear mine screaming love.

-
Tenebris Cor Traiecit is the second work of the Amare Tenebris project, and it's one of the most significant artwork of my life.
